@model SlideInfo.App.Models.MessengerViewModel
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http
@using SlideInfo.App.Constants
@using SlideInfo.App.Helpers

@if (Context.Session.GetString(SessionConstants.ALERT) != null)
{
    @Html.Raw(Context.Session.GetString(SessionConstants.ALERT))
    Context.Session.Remove(SessionConstants.ALERT);
}

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Messages";
}
<h2>@ViewData["Title"]</h2>
<hr />
<div ng-app="messenger">
    <div class="messenger" ng-controller="messengerController as vm">
        <div class="col-sm-3">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="custom-search-input">
                    <div class="input-group col-md-12">
                        <input type="text" class="search-query form-control" placeholder="Search..." />
                        <button class="btn btn-danger" type="button">
                            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul class="nav nav-tabs" ng-if="vm.showConversations">
                    <li ng-class="{'active' : !vm.showUsers}"><a href="#" ng-click="vm.showUsers = !vm.showUsers">Conversations</a></li>
                    <li ng-class="{'active' : vm.showUsers}"><a href="#" ng-click="vm.showUsers = !vm.showUsers">Users</a></li>
                </ul>

                <div class="member-list" ng-hide="vm.showUsers" ng-if="vm.showConversations">
                    <div class="member-link" ng-class="{'selected' : conversation.subject === vm.currentSubject}" ng-repeat="conversation in vm.conversations" id="{{conversation.subject}}">
                        <div class="media" ng-click="vm.getConversation(conversation.subject)">
                            <div class="media-left">
                                <img src="~/images/messenger_user.png" alt="User Avatar" width="40" class="img-circle">
                            </div>
                            <div class="media-body a">
                                <h4>
                                    {{conversation.Users}}
                                    <span class="status-icon"></span>
                                    <span class="badge pull-right flash animated" ng-show="conversation.UnreadMessagesCount > 0">{{conversation.UnreadMessagesCount}}</span>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="member-list" ng-show="vm.showUsers">
                    <div class="member-link" ng-class="{'selected' : user.Id === vm.currentReceiver.Id}" ng-repeat="user in vm.users" id="{{user.Id}}">
                        <div class="media" ng-click="vm.getConversation(user.PrivateConversationSubject)">
                            <div class="media-left">
                                <img src="~/images/messenger_user.png" alt="User Avatar" width="40" class="img-circle">
                            </div>
                            <div class="media-body a">
                                <h4>
                                    {{user.FullName}}
                                    <span class="status-icon"></span>
                                    <span class="badge pull-right flash animated" ng-show="user.UnreadMessagesCount > 0">{{user.UnreadMessagesCount}}</span>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!--chat_sidebar-->
        <div class="col-sm-9 message_section">
            <div class="row">

                <div class="chat-area" id="chat-area">
                    <div class="messages-inner" id="messages-inner">
                        <div class="messages-content" id="message-content">
                            <div class="message-wrapper" ng-repeat="message in vm.currentConversation" repeat-complete="vm.listDidRender()" id="{{message.Id}}" ng-class="message.FromId === vm.currentUser.Id ? 'me' : 'them'">
                                <div class="date-wrapper animated fadeIn">{{ message.DateSent | date: "dd.MM.yyyy HH:mm:ss"}}</div>
                                <div class="circle-wrapper animated bounceIn"></div>
                                <div class="text-wrapper animated fadeIn">{{ message.Content }}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!--chat_area-->
                <div class="message-write">
                    <textarea class="form-control message-input" id="message-input" placeholder="@ViewConstants.MESSAGE_TEXT_PLACEHOLDER" ng-model="vm.messageText" ng-keypress="vm.checkEnterPressed($event)"></textarea>
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <div class="chat-bottom">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-default pull-left" role="button">
                            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-upload" aria-hidden="true"></i> @ViewConstants.MESSAGE_ADD_ATTACHMENT
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" id="send-message" class="pull-right btn btn-success green-button" ng-click="vm.sendMessage()">
                            @ViewConstants.SEND_MESSAGE
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
@section scripts {

    <!-- jQuery -->
    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.js"></script>
    <!-- SignalR -->
    <script src="~/js/jquery.signalr-2.2.2.js"></script>
    <!--Reference the autogenerated SignalR hub script. -->
    <script src="~/signalr/hubs"></script>
    <!--SignalR script to update the chat page and send messages.-->
    <script src="/messenger/messenger.module.js"></script>
    <script src="/messenger/messenger.controller.js"></script>
    <script src="/messenger/messenger.service.js"></script>
    <script src="/messenger/repeat-complete-directive.js"></script>
}
